    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been babied since day one, kept spotless in the garage, and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
